 {"id":"bd-bpw","title":"Implement eager loading with automatic JOINs","description":"# Task: Implement Eager Loading with Automatic JOINs

## Context
Eager loading fetches related objects in the same query as the parent, using SQL JOINs. This avoids the N+1 problem entirely by loading relationships upfront.

## Design Goals
1. **Automatic JOIN generation**: From relationship metadata
2. **Selective loading**: Choose which relationships to eager-load
3. **Nested loading**: Load relationships of relationships
4. **Column aliasing**: Handle column name conflicts

